ase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"links\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 324}, {\"ngram\": \"our site\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"an affiliate commission\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up to our free weekly newsletter for exclusive competitions, offers and theatre ticket deals I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our free weekly newsletter\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"exclusive competitions\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"theatre ticket\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"deals\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"event\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"Evening Standard\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourprivacy notice\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom Daley's odds to take part in the next series of I am A Celebrity... Get Me Out Of Here have shot up after heconfirmed his retirement from divingafter competing at the 2024Olympics.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.338471909576078e-47, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"the next series\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"A Celebrity\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 652}, {\"ngram\": \"his retirement\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old athlete made his Olympics debut aged just 14 at the Beijing Games in 2008 and 16 years later has he won a silver medal at the Paris Games to add to his collection of three bronzes and one gold.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 30-year-old athlete\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympics debut\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beijing Games\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"his collection\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"three bronzes\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"one gold\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After confirming on Mondaythat he will be hanging up his speedos,entering the Australian jungle could be a next step.\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999692049594734, \"rank\": 2.2319031483354902e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mondaythat\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"his speedos\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"a next step\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest odds from Ladbrokes certainly agree, placing him at just 3/1 to appear on the next series when it returns in November hosted by Ant and Dec. A number of other former Olympians have given it a go over the years, including Sam Quek and Amir Khan.\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1333, \"end\": 1341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Quek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\"}, {\"begin\": 1346, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.910467671857008e-19, \"text\": \"Amir Khan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latest odds\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"Ladbrokes\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"the next series\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"Ant\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"A number\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"other former Olympians\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"a go\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley is also no stranger himself to reality TV after serving as a mentor on ITV show Splash from 2013-2014 where he attempted to teachcelebritieshow to dive.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1435, \"end\": 1438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\", \"score\": 0.931842604174716, \"rank\": 0.037963543887348274, \"text\": \"ITV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"no stranger\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"reality TV\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"a mentor\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Addressing his decision to make Paris his last Olympics, Daley toldBritish Vogue: \\\"It feels very, very surreal.\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999982251211, \"rank\": 1.7746724183460779e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt so incredibly nervous going into this, knowing it was my last Olympics.\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my last Olympics\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a lot of pressure and expectation.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"expectation\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was eager for it to be done\\u2026 but when I walked out, and saw my husband [Dustin Lance Black] and kids [Robbie and Phoenix] and my friends and family in the audience, I was like, you know what?\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1830, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dustin Lance Black\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my husband\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is exactly why I did this,\\\" he continued.\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am here, and no matter what happens in the competition itself, I am going to be happy.\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was emotional at the end, up there on the platform, knowing it was going to be my last competitive dive.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2117}, {\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"my last competitive dive\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I have to make the decision at some point, and it feels like the right time.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the right time to call it a day.\\\"\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsena